        "text_dmU4xi": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>Our Wave Spas App empowers you to take control of your hot tub experience right from the palm of your hand. </em></p><p><strong>Effortless Bubbles Control<br/></strong>Experience the epitome of indulgence as you effortlessly control the intensity of bubbles, tailoring your spa experience to perfection<br/><br/><strong>Smart Heating Scheduler<br/></strong>Transform your spa into a haven of warmth by programming it to preheat before your arrival. Let the welcoming embrace of perfectly heated water await you!<br/><br/><strong>Intuitive Filter Management<br/></strong>Luxuriate in the convenience of a glance as our app displays your filter's remaining capacity. Stay ahead with the knowledge of when to indulge in a fresh filter<br/><br/><strong>Temperature Mastery for Effortless Relaxation</strong><br/>Unwind with absolute control by effortlessly monitoring the current spa temperature. Seamlessly plan the perfect relaxation time, ensuring every moment in your spa is a retreat into luxury<br/><br/></p>",
